This excludes dependent territories and constiunt countries though, but includes UN members. This also excludes Vatican City, unrecognized states and Antarctica. The reason why Vatican City is not included is because it's too small. The reason why Antarctica is also not included is because it goes too south. The reason why unrecognized states are not included is because they are disputed. Some unrecognized states are not even recognized by UN members and only 1 state so far is not even recognized
